{"tid":649001,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"野餐拍到「靈異照」 上載照片同日竟撈獲女屍","createTime":"2018-05-01T07:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T07:58:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e98b1e1cea80a931fdbd7cdd907cd021425763","tid":649001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180501/58132379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58132379&d=gCz%2Bn9pUQ%2BW1BqbAcjAdyQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e5210f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58132379&h=ad7cefa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180501/58132379</a><br />\n<br />\n【個心離一離】野餐拍到「靈異照」 上載照片同日竟撈獲女屍<br />\n<br />\n472,027<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0501 07:06 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0501 00:02<br />\n<br />\n英國曼徹斯特（Manchester）一名女子與親友2011年到水庫野餐並拍照留念，多年後她始發現相中出現一隻「鬼手」，而正正在她上載相片到社交網當天，當局就在水庫撈到一具女屍，令整件事更添怪異。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n28歲特雷爾法（Rhynnice Trelfa）上周將相片上載至社交網，從中可見一名穿黑色背心的男子身旁出現一隻蒼白的「鬼手」，男子身後更見到有頭髮飛揚。<br />\n<br />\n網民質疑照片造假，但特雷爾法強調當時沒人在附近，她憶述：「我知道沒有人在我們背後，另一張相於數秒後拍攝，但就沒有拍到手」。她見到鬼手後說：「顫慄的感覺遍佈我的身體，我開始哭，喉頭哽住，渾身都起雞皮疙瘩，我嚇壞了。」<br />\n<br />\n她估計「鬼手」的出現帶來啟示，因為「鬼手」所指向的男子，就在數年後過身。<br />\n<br />\n特雷爾上載照片後，有幾位靈媒指出，「鬼手」與她前伴侶一位女性家人有關。詭異的是，她與爸爸一查之下，發現水庫曾發生多宗悲劇，她說：「就在我上載照片的同一天，照片拍攝的地點就發現一具女屍。」<br />\n<br />\n她不禁猜想：「我想問的問題是：這是來自另一邊的訊息？我相信照片中的靈魂與我們有某種聯繫。」她對自己拍到這張相感到興趣，又指她向來相信鬼神之說，但一直沒有經歷過。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525053704_4145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525053704_4145.jpg&h=3e1d67ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525053705_48c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525053705_48c7.jpg&h=4b88be61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525053707_0aae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525053707_0aae.jpg&h=e7f90917&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac6abdf067eede2af868d69ef304c0743b51475e","tid":649001,"uid":99742,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"最後果張最恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e27b76d352cc46b8e28853eab2bc7584716a78d","tid":649001,"uid":160166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"個肥仔r j?"},{"pid":"7768ebf5b78b4adaaccb142983c6d97dd6b935b7","tid":649001,"uid":21896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"肥佬隻手做緊咩"}]}